args "--unamed-opts --no-handle-error --long-help -a gand_args_info -f gand_parser"
usage "gandaux COMMAND [OPTION]..."
description "Helpers to bring the gandalf system into shape.
This is meant for the server side.

COMMAND may be one of:
  add     Add a symbol to the symbol index.
  build   Generate the symbol index.
  dump    Generate a dump of specified IDX file.
  get     Get a symbol from the symbol index.
"

